Sankalp Singh Projecty CSCI E104

Personalizing Text-to-Image Generation using Textual Inversion¶

Cloned the modified code from personal repository

we should run the code at V100 High Ram configuration and choose python 3 pip 23.3.2 version for all the dependencies

In [ ]:
!git clone https://github.com/sankalpsingh92/textual_inversion.git
!cp -r ./textual_inversion/* .

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import os
images = dir_list = os.listdir("./images/forks")
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(16, 16))
idx = 1
for imgfile in images:
  img = plt.imread("./images/forks/" + imgfile)
  fig.add_subplot(1, 6, idx)
  idx=idx+1
  plt.imshow(img)
